'''3rd age ranger kit''' is a set of [[3rd age equipment]], and is the third most powerful non-degradable [[Ranged armour]] in-game. All 3rd age range equipment requires level 65 [[Ranged]] to use with the armour also requiring level 45 [[Defence]] to wear. Players can obtain 3rd age range equipment through the completion of [[Clue scroll (hard)|hard]], [[Clue scroll (elite)|elite]], and [[Clue scroll (master)|master]] tier [[Treasure Trails]].

3rd age range armour has similar bonuses to [[black dragonhide armour]] except with higher [[magic defence]] bonuses. It has lower overall bonuses compared to those of [[Karil's equipment]] and [[Armadyl armour]], whilst also being outdamaged by [[Elite Void Knight equipment]].

